      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三月八日　高校卒業式の日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chime-03.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.333377
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "告白する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "好きです、付き合って下さい",
              "startTime": 117.0000013784,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 119.7000013784
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei011.m4a",
              "text": "えっ、と、突然……！？　\nあ、ありがとう……",
              "startTime": 119.7000013784,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "ああ、ずっと怜のことが好きだったんだ\n友達としてではなく\n恋人としてこれからも一緒にいたい",
              "startTime": 127.0333306428,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei012.m4a",
              "text": "私も{user}のことが……\nだ、大好きよ。だから……好きって\n言ってくれて、本当に嬉しい",
              "startTime": 135.2666751659,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei013.m4a",
              "text": "きっと{user}と付き合ったら\n毎日が楽しくて幸せだと思う",
              "startTime": 149.5333581086,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei014.m4a",
              "text": "でも……\n今はキャストになる夢を叶えたい気持ちが\n一番強いから付き合うことは出来ない",
              "startTime": 155.1666934765,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 165.3478277004
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "そっか……うん、そうだよな\n困らせるようなこと言っちゃってごめ――",
              "startTime": 166.1000074819,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 172.933339798
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei015.m4a",
              "text": "夢が叶った時には……\nちゃんと気持ちを伝えるから\n今度は私から告白する",
              "startTime": 172.933339798,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei016.m4a",
              "text": "好きです、{user}\n付き合って下さいって",
              "startTime": 181.6000084992,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "ははっ、じゃあ、早く付き合えるように\nこれからも怜のそばで\nしっかりサポートしないとだな",
              "startTime": 186.0666843212,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei017.m4a",
              "text": "ええ、これからも、これまで以上に\nよろしく頼むわ",
              "startTime": 195.3000176545,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "告白しない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "これからもよろしくな",
              "startTime": 200.933347936,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 202.7000146027
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei018.m4a",
              "text": "ええ、よろしくね\n一緒の大学に通えるの、楽しみだわ",
              "startTime": 202.7000146027,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei019.m4a",
              "text": "大学生になっても\n勉強を教えてくれる……？",
              "startTime": 209.5666934764,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "医学部の授業は\n高校に比べて難しくなりそうだけど\n俺に出来る範囲でサポートするよ",
              "startTime": 215.1666934764,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei020.m4a",
              "text": "ありがとう！\nキャストになる夢はまだ諦めていないけれど",
              "startTime": 221.7000268097,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei021.m4a",
              "text": "医者になって、趣味でダンスを続けるのも\nアリかな～って少しだけ思い始めたの",
              "startTime": 228.4000268097,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "どんな選択をしても\n怜ならきっと大丈夫だよ\n自分で選んだ道をしっかり進んでいける",
              "startTime": 235.9333581085,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei022.m4a",
              "text": "{user}が\nそう言ってくれるなら\nなんでも出来る気がしてきたわ",
              "startTime": 244.1333581085,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 248.1036983604
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei023.m4a",
              "text": "これからも……ずっと私の隣に居てよね\n……好きよ",
              "startTime": 248.9666782175,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 257.8000115508
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "え……今なんて？",
              "startTime": 257.8000115508,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei024.m4a",
              "text": "ふふっ。なんでもなーい\nファミレスでも寄って帰りましょー！",
              "startTime": 260.4666782175,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.133333377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "卒業まで、あっという間だったわね。特に\n{user}と過ごしたこの一年は",
      "startTime": 3.033333377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "寂しいか？",
      "startTime": 11.2000003616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5666667103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、あんまり\nだって、私達\n同じ大学に通うじゃない",
      "startTime": 12.5666667103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2666662653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったな。\n改めて、医学部合格おめでとう\nお父さんも少しは認めてくれたか？",
      "startTime": 20.2666662653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、とても喜んでくれたわ\nダンスを勝手に辞めさせたことも\n謝ってくれたの",
      "startTime": 28.333332932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2999980728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんの口から\n「今まで悪かった」って言葉を\n聞いた時は、とても気持ちが良かったわ",
      "startTime": 36.2999980728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かった\nこれからもダンスは続けるのか？",
      "startTime": 44.0333314061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "テーマパークの再オーディションには\n落ちてしまったけれど……",
      "startTime": 48.6666647394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.6666601617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりダンスは好きだから\n医者になるための\n勉強もしながら続けようと思っているわ",
      "startTime": 52.6666601617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスを続けるって聞けて安心したよ\nそういえば今日誕生日だったよな\nおめでとう",
      "startTime": 59.9999957839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 67.0408802787
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7666665195
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.7666665195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_08_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "覚えてくれていたのね！　ありがとう",
      "startTime": 67.7666665195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
